	(6, '租机流程', '租机说明', '<p style="outline: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.5em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 153) 0.005em 0.005em 0.025em !important;"><span style="outline: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 153) 0.005em 0.005em 0.025em !important;">注册：新企业用户进入艾特租网站，按平台指示进行注册登录，获取您的用户中心。</span></p><p style="outline: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 153) 0.005em 0.005em 0.025em !important;"><br style="outline: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2em; text-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 153) 0.005em 0.005em 0.025em !important;"/></p><p style="outline: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.5em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 153) 0.005em 0.005em 0.025em !important;"><span style="outline: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 153) 0.005em 0.005em 0.025em !important;"><span style="outline: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; max-width: 100%; text-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 153) 0.005em 0.005em 0.025em !important;">申请免押金额度：用户在注册过程中