rong style="outline: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; max-width: 100%; text-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 153) 0.005em 0.005em 0.025em !important; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot; !important;"><span style="outline: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; text-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 153) 0.005em 0.005em 0.025em !important;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="outline: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-indent: 32px; text-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 153) 0.005em 0.005em 0.025em !important; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot; !important;"><span style="outline: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; line-height: 24px; text-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 153) 0.005em 0.005em 0.025em !important;">1）逾期1个月未支付按合同或订单约定应支付的费用，包括但不限于租金、提前退还产生的服务费或维修费；</span></p><p style="outline: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-indent: 32px; text-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 153) 0.005em 0.005em 0.025em !important; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot; !important;"><span style="outline: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; line-height: 24px; text-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 153) 0.005em 0.005em 0.025em !important;">2）按约定应当归还设备，但拒不归还，或超过1个月未归还；</span></p><p style="outline: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-indent: 32px; text-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 153) 0.005em 0.005em 0.025em !important; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot; !important;"><span style="outline: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 153) 0.005em 0.005em 0.025em !important;"><strong style="outline: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; max-width: 100%; text-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 153) 0.005em 0.005em 0.025em !important; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot; !important;"><span style="outline: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; text-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 153) 0.005em 0.005em 0.025em !important;">2.承租方同意，对于因出现违反本合同约定内容被认定为失信客户的，艾特租将有权利采取包括但不限于以下的措施：</span></strong><strong style="outline: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; max-width: 100%; text-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 153) 0.005em 0.005em 0.025em !important; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot; !important;"><span style="outline: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; text-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 153) 0.005em 0.005em 0.025em !important;"></span></strong></span></p><p style="outline: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-indent: 32px; text-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 153) 0.005em 0.005em 0.025em !important; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot; !important;"><span style="outline: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; line-height: 24px; text-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 153) 0.005em 0.005em 0.025em !important;">1）不接受失信客户的服务需求；</span></p><p style="outline: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-indent: 32px; text-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 153) 0.005em 0.005em 