ow: rgb(153, 153, 153) 0.005em 0.005em 0.025em !important;">2）按约定应当归还设备，但拒不归还；</span></p><p style="outline: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: auto; margin-bottom: auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.5em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 153) 0.005em 0.005em 0.025em !important;"><span style="outline: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 153) 0.005em 0.005em 0.025em !important;">3）在租期结束前提前归还设备，但不按协议支付随租随还服务费或违约金；</span></p><p style="outline: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: auto; margin-bottom: auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.5em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 153) 0.005em 0.005em 0.025em !important;"><span style="outline: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 153) 0.005em 0.005em 0.025em !important;">4）归还的设备严重损坏，但拒不按协议偿付维修费用。</span></p><p style="outline: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: auto; margin-bottom: auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.5em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 153) 0.005em 0.005em 0.025em !important;"><strong style="outline: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; max-width: 100%; text-shadow: rgb(153, 153, 153) 0.005em 0.005em 0.025em !important;"><span style="outline: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent